---
import AboutHeroImage from '../assets/blog-placeholder-about.jpg';
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="Admissions 2026-27 | Saraswati Shiksha Niketan Inter College, Ghaziabad"
	description="Admission process, eligibility, documents, fee structure, and FAQs for Saraswati Shiksha Niketan Inter College, Vijay Nagar, Ghaziabad. Apply now for Nursery to Class 12."
	pubDate={new Date('August 08 2021')}
	heroImage={AboutHeroImage}
>
<section class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="breadcrumb"><a href="/">Home</a> / <span>Admissions</span></div>
      <h1>Admissions 2026-27</h1>
      <p>Everything you need to know to apply — process, eligibility, documents, fees, and key dates, in one place.</p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a href="#inquiry" class="btn btn-primary">Start Application <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"/></svg></a>
        <a href="#prospectus" class="btn btn-outline">Download Prospectus <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 15v4a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-4"/><path d="M7 10l5 5 5-5"/><path d="M12 15V3"/></svg></a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-head center">
        <span class="eyebrow">How It Works</span>
        <h2>Our Admission Process</h2>
        <p class="lede" style="margin-inline:auto;">A simple, transparent four-step journey from inquiry to enrollment.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-4">
        <div class="card reveal"><div class="icon-badge"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="m22 2-7 20-4-9-9-4Z"/><path d="M22 2 11 13"/></svg></div><h3>1. Submit Inquiry</h3><p>Fill the online inquiry form or visit our admissions desk with your child's details.</p></div>
        <div class="card reveal"><div class="icon-badge"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polygon points="16.24 7.76 14.12 14.12 7.76 16.24 9.88 9.88 16.24 7.76"/></svg></div><h3>2. Campus Visit</h3><p>Tour our classrooms, labs, and facilities, and meet the relevant class coordinator.</p></div>
        <div class="card reveal"><div class="icon-badge"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M14.5 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V7.5z"/><path d="M14 2v6h6"/><path d="M9 13h6"/><path d="M9 17h6"/></svg></div><h3>3. Assessment / Interaction</h3><p>An age-appropriate interaction (Nursery-Class 2) or basic assessment (Class 3 onward).</p></div>
        <div class="card reveal"><div class="icon-badge"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg></div><h3>4. Confirm Admission</h3><p>Submit documents, pay admission fee, and receive your child's enrollment confirmation.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section alt">
    <div class="container split">
      <div class="reveal">
        <span class="eyebrow">Who Can Apply</span>
        <h2>Eligibility Criteria</h2>
        <table class="data-table mt-lg">
          <thead><tr><th>Class</th><th>Minimum Age (as of 31 March)</th></tr></thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr><td>Nursery</td><td>3 years</td></tr>
            <tr><td>LKG</td><td>4 years</td></tr>
            <tr><td>UKG</td><td>5 years</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Class 1</td><td>6 years</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Class 2 – 8</td><td>Age-appropriate + transfer certificate</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Class 9 &amp; 11</td><td>Passed previous class + subject continuity for Class 11 streams</td></tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
      <div class="reveal">
        <span class="eyebrow">Come Prepared</span>
        <h2>Required Documents</h2>
        <ul class="check-list mt-lg">
          <li><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg> Birth certificate (original + photocopy)</li>
          <li><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg> Previous school's report card / mark sheet</li>
          <li><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg> Transfer certificate (for Class 2 and above)</li>
          <li><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg> Aadhaar card of the student</li>
          <li><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg> Passport-size photographs (4 copies)</li>
          <li><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg> Address proof of parent / guardian</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-head center">
        <span class="eyebrow">Plan Ahead</span>
        <h2>Admission Timeline — 2026-27</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-4">
        <div class="event-card reveal"><div class="event-date"><div class="d">01</div><div class="m">Dec</div></div><div><h4>Applications Open</h4><p>Inquiry forms and prospectus available online and at the front office.</p></div></div>
        <div class="event-card reveal"><div class="event-date"><div class="d">15</div><div class="m">Jan</div></div><div><h4>Campus Visits &amp; Interactions</h4><p>Scheduled tours and student interactions begin by appointment.</p></div></div>
        <div class="event-card reveal"><div class="event-date"><div class="d">28</div><div class="m">Feb</div></div><div><h4>Admission Confirmation</h4><p>Offer letters issued; seat confirmed on fee payment and document submission.</p></div></div>
        <div class="event-card reveal"><div class="event-date"><div class="d">01</div><div class="m">Apr</div></div><div><h4>Session Begins</h4><p>New academic session 2026-27 commences for all classes.</p></div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section alt" id="prospectus">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-head">
        <span class="eyebrow">Investment in Education</span>
        <h2>Fee Information</h2>
        <p class="lede">Our fee structure is designed to be transparent and predictable for families planning ahead. For the complete, current fee schedule, download our prospectus or speak with our admissions desk.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-2" style="align-items:center;">
        <table class="data-table">
          <thead><tr><th>Level</th><th>Admission Fee (one-time)</th><th>Tuition (per month, approx.)</th></tr></thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr><td>Nursery – UKG</td><td>&#8377;8,000</td><td>&#8377;1,800</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Class 1 – 5</td><td>&#8377;9,500</td><td>&#8377;2,100</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Class 6 – 8</td><td>&#8377;10,500</td><td>&#8377;2,400</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Class 9 – 10</td><td>&#8377;12,000</td><td>&#8377;2,800</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Class 11 – 12</td><td>&#8377;13,500</td><td>&#8377;3,200</td></tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
        <div class="card">
          <div class="icon-badge"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M14.5 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V7.5z"/><path d="M14 2v6h6"/><path d="M9 13h6"/><path d="M9 17h6"/></svg></div>
          <h3>Download Our Prospectus</h3>
          <p>Get the complete admissions brochure with detailed fee structure, curriculum overview, and campus information.</p>
          <div class="hero-actions" style="margin-top:1.2rem;">
            <a href="#" class="btn btn-dark btn-sm">Download Prospectus <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 15v4a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-4"/><path d="M7 10l5 5 5-5"/><path d="M12 15V3"/></svg></a>
            <a href="#" class="btn btn-outline btn-sm" style="color:var(--color-primary);border-color:var(--color-primary);">Download Brochure <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 15v4a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-4"/><path d="M7 10l5 5 5-5"/><path d="M12 15V3"/></svg></a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-head">
        <span class="eyebrow">Good to Know</span>
        <h2>Admission Guidelines</h2>
      </div>
      <ul class="check-list two-col-list">
        <li><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg> Admission is subject to seat availability in each section.</li>
        <li><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg> Sibling admissions receive priority scheduling for interactions.</li>
        <li><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg> Mid-session admissions are considered case-by-case, subject to seats.</li>
        <li><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg> Admission fee is non-refundable once a seat is confirmed.</li>
        <li><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg> Transport and uniform are arranged separately after enrollment.</li>
        <li><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg> All original documents must be verified before the session begins.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section alt" id="faq">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-head center">
        <span class="eyebrow">Common Questions</span>
        <h2>Admissions FAQ</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="accordion" style="max-width:800px;margin-inline:auto;">
        <div class="accordion-item">
          <button class="accordion-trigger" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="faq1">Is there an entrance test for Nursery admission?<span><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 5v14"/><path d="M5 12h14"/></svg></span></button>
          <div class="accordion-panel" id="faq1" style="max-height:200px;"><p>No formal test — we conduct a short, friendly interaction to understand the child's comfort level and readiness for school.</p></div>
        </div>
        <div class="accordion-item">
          <button class="accordion-trigger" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq2">Do you accept mid-year transfer admissions?<span><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 5v14"/><path d="M5 12h14"/></svg></span></button>
          <div class="accordion-panel" id="faq2"><p>Yes, subject to seat availability in the relevant class and a review of the student's previous academic record and transfer certificate.</p></div>
        </div>
        <div class="accordion-item">
          <button class="accordion-trigger" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq3">What streams are offered in Class 11?<span><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 5v14"/><path d="M5 12h14"/></svg></span></button>
          <div class="accordion-panel" id="faq3"><p>We offer Science (Physics, Chemistry, Maths/Biology), Commerce, and Humanities streams, subject to Class 10 performance and seat availability.</p></div>
        </div>
        <div class="accordion-item">
          <button class="accordion-trigger" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq4">Is transportation available from all areas of Ghaziabad?<span><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 5v14"/><path d="M5 12h14"/></svg></span></button>
          <div class="accordion-panel" id="faq4"><p>Our bus routes cover most parts of Vijay Nagar and neighbouring areas. Please check specific route availability with our transport desk.</p></div>
        </div>
        <div class="accordion-item">
          <button class="accordion-trigger" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq5">Are scholarships available for meritorious students?<span><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 5v14"/><path d="M5 12h14"/></svg></span></button>
          <div class="accordion-panel" id="faq5"><p>Yes, merit-based fee concessions are available for outstanding academic and sports performance, reviewed annually by the management committee.</p></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" id="inquiry">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-head center">
        <span class="eyebrow">Ready to Begin?</span>
        <h2>Admission Inquiry Form</h2>
        <p class="lede" style="margin-inline:auto;">Complete the form below and our admissions team will reach out with next steps and available slots.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="form-card reveal" style="max-width:760px;margin-inline:auto;">
        <div class="form-success" role="status"></div>
        <form data-validate>
          <div class="form-row">
            <div class="field"><label for="a-sname">Student's Name</label><input type="text" id="a-sname" required><span class="error-msg">Please enter the student's name.</span></div>
            <div class="field"><label for="a-dob">Date of Birth</label><input type="date" id="a-dob" required><span class="error-msg">Please enter date of birth.</span></div>
          </div>
          <div class="form-row">
            <div class="field"><label for="a-pname">Parent / Guardian Name</label><input type="text" id="a-pname" required><span class="error-msg">Please enter parent's name.</span></div>
            <div class="field"><label for="a-phone">Phone Number</label><input type="tel" id="a-phone" data-phone required><span class="error-msg">Please enter a valid 10-digit number.</span></div>
          </div>
          <div class="form-row">
            <div class="field"><label for="a-email">Email Address</label><input type="email" id="a-email" required><span class="error-msg">Please enter a valid email.</span></div>
            <div class="field"><label for="a-class">Class Applying For</label>
              <select id="a-class" required>
                <option value="">Select a class</option>
                <option>Nursery</option><option>LKG</option><option>UKG</option>
                <option>Class 1 - 5</option><option>Class 6 - 8</option>
                <option>Class 9 - 10</option><option>Class 11 - 12</option>
              </select>
              <span class="error-msg">Please select a class.</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="field"><label for="a-msg">Additional Message (optional)</label><textarea id="a-msg" rows="3"></textarea></div>
          <button class="btn btn-primary btn-block" type="submit">Submit Admission Inquiry <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="m22 2-7 20-4-9-9-4Z"/><path d="M22 2 11 13"/></svg></button>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
